Please create New Policy in Azure Policy and copy the JSON to the Policy Rule.
Please search for "dataCollectionEndpointId", see it is empty, and add the DataCollection endpoint ID from the JSON view (in the overview screen)
Please give it the relevent name: [Custom]: Configure Association to link Microsoft Defender for Cloud Data Collection Rule with Data Collection Endpoint for VM
Please set the relevent scope and save the policy.
Note: if you have multiple regions, the policy should be created per region with the relevent dataCollectionEndpointId
